XP :: 100

A threatening Ethos remnant is nearby. Defeat it and claim your reward!

---mobdefinition_Miniboss Forge Two---
ID :: minibossforgetwo
Prefab :: minibossforge
Range Behavior :: [[Stationary]]
Bounding Box :: 0 2.73 2.5 3.0
Type :: Miniboss
Speed :: 0
Interaction Timer :: 0.1
Interaction Label :: Activate
Options :: noaggronearby
Loot :: [[Miniboss Forge Two]]

---loottable_Miniboss Forge Two---
[[701 Damage Pulse]] @ 15.0
[[651 Tanky Pulse]] @ 15.0
[[604 Suppression Pulse]] @ 15.0
[[602 Shock Pulse]] @ 15.0

---script_minibossforgetwo_Monster---

if is_undefined(scriptVars["eventActive"]) {
    scriptVars["eventActive"] = false
    scriptVars["timeSinceActivated"] = 0.0
    addAuraToEntity(myEntityId, "Permanent Immunity", 0, myEntityId)
}

if !scriptVars["eventActive"] && len(usedByEntities) > 0 {
	scriptVars["eventActive"] = true
	triggerAnimation(myEntityId, "Activate")
	summonEntity("minibosstwo", entityPosition(myEntityId), monsterLevel(myEntityId))
}

if scriptVars["eventActive"] {
    scriptVars["timeSinceActivated"] += delta
    if scriptVars["timeSinceActivated"] > 1.5 {
        setCollisionLayer(myEntityId, CollisionLayerDynamic)
    }
}

---mob_MinibossTwo---
ID :: minibosstwo
Prefab :: miniboss
Range Behavior :: [[Melee Ranged]]
Bounding Box :: 0.0 0.3 1.0 1.0
Type :: Miniboss
Speed :: 1300
Options :: manualpathing

//Accelerating Shot Phase Attacks

